data.description: Centrally located 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bath townhome in the highly sought after subdivision of SANDALWOOD LAKES! This newly painted home features a spacious living room, an open kitchen concept and a bathroom downstairs. Each large bedroom has a sliding glass door and a private balcony overlooking the patio. The large private fenced patio is perfect for creating your private space for entertainment and gardening. Minutes away from the Ballpark of the Palm Beaches, downtown West Palm Beach, close to I95, beaches, parks, the Palm Beach Outlet and several recreational facilities. Make this your new home today!
